title: The Celestine Prophecy (2006) Full DVD
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0398842/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0398842/</a>

(Pronounced Cele-steene from the Pope's name, like Augustine.)

Adaptation of James Redfield's novel about the search for a sacred manuscript in the Peruvian rain forest. I was very inspired by the book and less by the film, but it was interesting to see all the exotic places described by Redfield.

This is not my rip, I found it on the net using PirateBay's tracker, so I thought it should be represented here. Alas, the French soundtrack and subs have been deleted from this copy, but the English subs may be handy because some Spanish is spoken.

Tip: Press 'Menu' to escape trailer at beginning.
